OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mix of sunshine and showers
OL,6,Facross northern areas today, with some
OL,7,Fheavy and a risk of hail. Drier and
OL,8,Fbrighter further south, although a few
OL,9,Fshowers developing across Wales and
OL,10,Fthe Midlands into the afternoon.
OL,11,FPleasant in any sunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers gradually easing from
OL,14,Fthe west tonight leaving plenty of
OL,15,Fclear skies across much of the
OL,16,Fcountry. A colder night with a frost
OL,17,Fin places, especially in the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
